title: and Lala's Gusbands Logan & Leo
description:
Lala’s gusbands, Logan and Leo, grab the mic and bring the party to the podcast complete with leap frogs, Beyonce moves, and dancing for dollars! Hear the stories from the foursome’s recent Palm Springs vacay, Lala’s first intro to Logan and Leo, their wild Disneyland adventure, and who is going to be in charge of Baby Girl Emmett when the daytime adventure trio expands to four! Plus, Lala gets real about pregnancy hormones and acne, epidurals and sobriety, the sale of her childhood home, and Scheana Shay.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
